WEBVTT

1
00:26:49.700 --> 00:26:54.160 
拜托  就今晚这一次  别谈论任何不好的事情
Please, tonight for once, I don't want anything bad talked about.

2
00:26:54.300 --> 00:26:55.600 
好好享用这一餐
Enjoy your meal.

3
00:26:55.730 --> 00:26:58.000 
好  那么我来说件有趣的事
fine,Then I'll tell you something funny.

4
00:26:58.140 --> 00:26:59.630 
你们知道罗席嘉先生吗
You know who I mean by Dr. Raszeja?

5
00:26:59.770 --> 00:27:01.400 
-那位军医?  -对 军医
- The surgeon? - The surgeon.

6
00:27:01.540 --> 00:27:03.600 
