for some reason and not ask me why

7
00:27:03.680 --> 00:27:06.340 
德国人允许他到犹太人区做手术
The Germans allowed him into the ghetto to perform an operation.

8
00:27:06.480 --> 00:27:07.600 
对犹太人动刀?
On a Jew?

9
00:27:07.680 --> 00:27:09.610 
